## Verify Manually

You can reproduce these results using any SHA-256 tool. For example, using Python:

```python
import hashlib, unicodedata
beacon = "<%= @decision.lottery_beacon_randomness %>"
<% @decision.results.each do |result| -%>
title = <%= result.option_title.inspect %>
print(hashlib.sha256((beacon + unicodedata.normalize("NFC", title)).encode()).hexdigest())
<% end -%>
```

Each output should match the sort key shown above for that <%= @decision.is_lottery? ? 'entry' : 'option' %>.
